{"tid":118171,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"500typeEVA新幹線問題","createTime":"2017-02-12T20:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T02:59:19.000Z","uid":2630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a02d91569f906dcf3252ffa3baae16858c9dbc1f","tid":118171,"uid":2630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T20:14:16.000Z","msg":"小弟係EVA死忠<br />\n去過幾次日本<br />\n但未坐過新幹線<br />\n所以好驚搞錯車飛啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我3月尾就去關西8日<br />\n頭7日都同朋友一齊<br />\n第8日得自己一個<br />\n就好想朝拜下呢架EVA新幹線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有google過啲遊記睇<br />\n但都唔係好清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以下有幾個問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我都只係想參觀部列車<br />\n1. 想問係咪買圖裡面8500yen嗰個pass就夠？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ly62Ph3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLy62Ph3.jpg&h=dd6c343b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.另外我係咪只可以喺岡山落車？<br />\n   可唔可以喺姫路落？<br />\n<br />\n3. 當我上咗車，喺岡山或者姫路落咗車<br />\n    我用返8500yen嗰個pass<br />\n    可唔可以坐返新幹線或者JR返大阪？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能我啲問題有啲膠<br />\n亦都有啲1999<br />\n但我真係好想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哭求巴打們幫幫手解決我疑難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825a5b7f10f2544fe4fdcbddbd16ce6f80cc00f5","tid":118171,"uid":42881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T20:27:55.000Z","msg":"廣域版8500JPY可以搭了<br />\n<br />\nPASS內任意上落，所以你係岡山上/大阪上，姬路落係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n但回程應該只可以搭一般新幹線，因為EVA一日得一對來回"},{"pid":"cc5cc1f51cd9f7e5eda900edcf675d9f713193d3","tid":118171,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T22:44:59.000Z","msg":"記得去博多端車頭拎postcard"},{"pid":"cd687bce5889b058cd68850bd3afd7dafc8e04d4","tid":118171,"uid":2630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T23:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣域版8500JPY可以搭了<br />\n<br />\nPASS內任意上落，所以你係岡山上/大阪上，姬路落係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n但回程應該只可以搭一般新幹線，因為EVA一日得一對來回</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n清晣曬<br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e0cdb4467fbd2d4b35839beec0350bb30703c4","tid":118171,"uid":2630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T23:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得去博多端車頭拎postcard</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有postcard咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffde929f1325add1b244d43dbe0ea476681c960","tid":118171,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>記得去博多端車頭拎postcard</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有postcard咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀, 我上次坐 去頭卡參觀有得送呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090233_d993f65f2c26888f87caf61b52e12af6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090233_d993f65f2c26888f87caf61b52e12af6.jpg&h=b4009e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090234_d993f65f2c26888f87caf61b52e12af6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090234_d993f65f2c26888f87caf61b52e12af6.jpg&h=41f567a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090234_6aa021a6319924dec30e97a0db2e8a36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090234_6aa021a6319924dec30e97a0db2e8a36.jpg&h=b4efeb4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjQN6bT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjQN6bT.jpg&h=58509ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CzrM81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CzrM81.jpg&h=bcd9d3e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ff82bfd8347fd19057dc258aa73077c546b45e4","tid":118171,"uid":70004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:03:46.000Z","msg":"留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce29d64fbbff88a177c8a0e6264f12ff8552377","tid":118171,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:05:12.000Z","msg":"呢架新幹線本身都超型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n襯埋eva真係一流"},{"pid":"f3f1c029eebbeab9049306bac30e3856127373f6","tid":118171,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090557_9f2b0d9309ea6d3eb4ddf24bad10f994.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090557_9f2b0d9309ea6d3eb4ddf24bad10f994.jpg&h=39d5ab6f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090559_89334a0d3ca2975ef1d3e4b3bac50a50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090559_89334a0d3ca2975ef1d3e4b3bac50a50.jpg&h=01672913&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090602_2de972cdecf0ee8dec63ec1e755720bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090602_2de972cdecf0ee8dec63ec1e755720bb.jpg&h=182991cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GRMo0f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGRMo0f6.jpg&h=71d49fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090609_bdbf35333d2e5b5c46a7070ba689fba5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090609_bdbf35333d2e5b5c46a7070ba689fba5.jpg&h=4a23612e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n博多"},{"pid":"742ce79caba6a89cd6e2defb32b6ea61ca9b3c94","tid":118171,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/614P0xj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F614P0xj.jpg&h=d17700a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090827_d945b3c73505ad51879d71ac26e32ed3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090827_d945b3c73505ad51879d71ac26e32ed3.jpg&h=92baa990&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1nb0yk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1nb0yk.jpg&h=4683e781&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/309Bgw9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F309Bgw9.jpg&h=bfaf6d60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090832_6a1512d0a2ebc22051d125fab7aa2af9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090832_6a1512d0a2ebc22051d125fab7aa2af9.jpg&h=dd292e85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c6b5254b2d5140a28b7b5dcf079dd3fe56b78ad","tid":118171,"uid":34091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:14:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.500type-eva.jp/entry/timetable.html#timetable\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.500type-eva.jp%2Fentry%2Ftimetable.html%23timetable&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=66cc2fba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.500type-eva.jp/entry/timetable.html#timetable</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打俾你做個參考<br />\n<br />\n如果你得一日自己去玩<br />\n又要去機場<br />\n建議唔好搭太遠<br />\n俾盡去埋姬路<br />\n程車都夠時間參觀架車"},{"pid":"b29b5bb6ba59e19d90ab397597db0b98ec37061d","tid":118171,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.500type-eva.jp/entry/timetable.html#timetable\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.500type-eva.jp%2Fentry%2Ftimetable.html%23timetable&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=66cc2fba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.500type-eva.jp/entry/timetable.html#timetable</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打俾你做個參考<br />\n<br />\n如果你得一日自己去玩<br />\n又要去機場<br />\n建議唔好搭太遠<br />\n俾盡去埋姬路<br />\n程車都夠時間參觀架車</blockquote><br />\n搭單問埋<br />\n<br />\n即係我可以係岡山上12:40個班車落廣島？？"},{"pid":"20afae0411eff87b2e8e1fb3b3a620e14c5384ce","tid":118171,"uid":2630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>記得去博多端車頭拎postcard</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有postcard咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀, 我上次坐 去頭卡參觀有得送呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090233_d993f65f2c26888f87caf61b52e12af6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090233_d993f65f2c26888f87caf61b52e12af6.jpg&h=b4009e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090234_d993f65f2c26888f87caf61b52e12af6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090234_d993f65f2c26888f87caf61b52e12af6.jpg&h=41f567a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/090234_6aa021a6319924dec30e97a0db2e8a36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F090234_6aa021a6319924dec30e97a0db2e8a36.jpg&h=b4efeb4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjQN6bT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjQN6bT.jpg&h=58509ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CzrM81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CzrM81.jpg&h=bcd9d3e1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇圖都已經好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去頭卡參觀係咪要抽中個A賞先去到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716a84dff60da7e8261ad7a157f7a2751982c9f9","tid":118171,"uid":2630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.500type-eva.jp/entry/timetable.html#timetable\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.500type-eva.jp%2Fentry%2Ftimetable.html%23timetable&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=66cc2fba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.500type-eva.jp/entry/timetable.html#timetable</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打俾你做個參考<br />\n<br />\n如果你得一日自己去玩<br />\n又要去機場<br />\n建議唔好搭太遠<br />\n俾盡去埋姬路<br />\n程車都夠時間參觀架車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThx巴打<br />\n我夜晚9點坐夜行巴去東京<br />\n所以我都怕時間會有啲趕<br />\n但姫路落到就應該無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95267d43a49817aa1002cb884194d6884fc1b03f","tid":118171,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"要坐EVA駕駛倉要抽<br />\n入一號車而家好似唔駛抽"},{"pid":"6f6b27c909b7c4fb74350d1b00ed303bd61e86e0","tid":118171,"uid":2630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要坐EVA駕駛倉要抽<br />\n入一號車而家好似唔駛抽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fc0c387c204e7949e76a6474284611cca6ba66","tid":118171,"uid":32012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"留明 六月底去搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}